      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "今天没课，刚睡醒",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我刚睁开眼睛，就马上回你信息了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你要是不听他的话，按照规章制度正常时间上班会有什么影响？好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "会不会穿小鞋？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我不知道，但我觉得应该会",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "还是别赌了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你的意思是我只能忍吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:04",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "零零后整顿职场是骗零零后的谎言啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "除非零零后有说走就走的决心，不然只能忍着吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "唉，还是怪我自己",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "别怪你自己了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "要怪就怪油滑利己的中层领导",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "怪不遵守劳动法的职场大环境",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "好绝望啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉每个地方都一样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "就算我换了一个公司也不会好多少",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:06",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "稍微人性化一点，公司总有的吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "像那种比如老板年轻一点，领导层也年轻一点的公司？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我也没体验过，但我，如果我们每一代如果我们这一代成长起来混入了管理层",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:07",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "职场环境可能会大变样，距离我们理想中的职场会接近一些",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:08",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "唉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "唉，那我要等到什么时候？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "等到我七老八十的时候？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "那也太绝望了吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "说不定下一家公司就是了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:09",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我要去做个早饭",
